Stepsize (GUI item property)
============================

??

This is a synonym to the [step](Step\_(GUI\_item\_property)) property.

This property is restricted to the [sliderDef](SliderDef\_(GUI\_item\_type)) item type.

Syntax
------

`stepsize `*`value`*

Default value
-------------

`Unknown`

Example(s)
----------

`stepsize   0.5`


